Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:29.93,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}此刻依然无限光芒照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:33.44,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}星空闪烁的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:37.47,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}不计其数的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:43.80,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}如今依然等待着你去实现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:48.51,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}所以迈步前进吧
