Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:51.19,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}不安的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:53.73,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}寻回的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.83,0:18:57.06,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}即便是无心的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:19:00.88,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}秋色的风
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:04.62,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}用老成的足迹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:07.21,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}将逝去的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.61,0:19:10.31,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}教给了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:13.68,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}来来往往
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:17.12,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}思考烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:24.99,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那唯一的真相
