Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.64,0:00:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.91,0:00:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早也练剑了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.36,0:00:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有打工呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.46,0:00:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是忙碌的青春
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.25,0:00:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没看书啊 好稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且很开心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.61,0:00:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近拓人君和班长很要好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.08,0:00:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人在丹治古卡拉OK打工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来那么开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.25,0:00:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有什么好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:00:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.48,0:01:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等考试完了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.97,0:01:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡边太太会再开派对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.35,0:01:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以拼桌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.37,0:01:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.54,0:01:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.37,0:01:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和年轻的石野老师单独吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是传什么绯闻就对不住人家了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 和学园长传绯闻可是我的荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这三位是我班上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.23,0:01:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤君和津名志君是戏剧社的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.69,0:01:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是他们的顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.22,0:01:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松山君是棒球社的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.51,0:01:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得是捕手？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.35,0:01:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是学园长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:02:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海报还贴着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.23,0:02:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿记得取掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.36,0:02:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好收拾善后了 戏剧才算结束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看了那场戏剧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长是远藤同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直都是那样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 远藤同学想要表现的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些连我也无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她的戏剧该怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种穿透力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对她的未来也抱有很大期待
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.43,0:02:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过实际感觉怎么样 须方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那场吻戏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说扬卷是你未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不介意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是演戏嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这么老成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:02:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擅长演出给定的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而要不要去演给定的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终是由自己决定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这句话 以前好像也说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃炸土豆饼不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～水平又提高了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长也一直夸我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱中的少女真可爱哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有亲亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长说要去东京的大学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:04:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我毕业了要不要也去东京呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要出岛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没决定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选…
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近和拓人君很要好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君的确是个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在店里也努力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我婶婶好像也完全成了他的迷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古式阿姨？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说拓人君比去年再婚的老公还好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是只对唯一看中的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专心一意就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和婶婶 和你都不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确很少见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长心情这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你怎么把他挖来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉醉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想过你就是行长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就是秘书了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.94,0:07:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前他一直拒绝我们的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么改变了他的心意？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意的话直接问他不就好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种意义上或许是最可怕的类型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 信悟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:07:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时生？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了个好长的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 是怎样的梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得约定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.15,0:08:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界无法让我长成我理想的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我停止了成长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可这样会变得更痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有自己被留在原地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时生不在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我需要你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我会更安心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的给时生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次由我来做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫长的美梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞台似乎开幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛要全球恐慌了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商人真是眼疾手快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤君和津名志君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来似乎都抱有极大的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的青春都会有烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 他们没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何问题都会自己解决然后成长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们有这种坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想永远看着这片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后随时都可以看的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 今天的天空只有今天能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后我们一定会看到比这更美的别样天空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下最后的祭典上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Samekh的驭星者就必然会列席了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是秋风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一起单独来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉真是不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆日死神社吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神社遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这里不再是神社也不过是不久前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾祖母那代还是正经的神社呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆日死巫女和皆水巫女一样是表巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说当时岛上的人们还都很敬重的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照进藤家的家规
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和须方君结婚的巫女说不定是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.78,0:12:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使和子从这个世界上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概你也会一直思念着她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当那家伙知道我是逆日死巫女的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他不会直接威胁我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他给人的感觉就是只要有意随时可以杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而有一天我突然醒悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.73,0:13:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要装作顺从他 打破了封印就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你就能成为真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为你而生的巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.62,0:13:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你的封印不解除
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都会成为下一世代 下一时代的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你诞生在了这个时代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为命中注定的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐与我…永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的银河中 刚才闪耀着最美的繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,okito
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立下永恒誓约的逆日死咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠都
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在已经不害怕任何事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆日死大人是绮罗星十字团的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.43,0:15:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要杀了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们继承了暗杀Samekh驭星者的奥义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻正是运用那力量之时…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷您太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事我根本做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷您明明知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一直…一直对少爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷回应了逆日死大人的心意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长 可能是今晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若有个万一就按原计划进行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机场也先联络上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人 万一是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:17:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚零时空间的封印可能要解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时位于零点的这个岛本身 及周围环境
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都很可能被卷入物理性变动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受巫女封印影响 附近火山也可能会喷发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视情况要将附近的人都引导来这艘船上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开岛去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.11,0:17:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让岛民都乘上这艘船吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们以为我为什么要买这么大一艘船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常时刻你们也要帮忙引导岛民避难
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然须方说不用付房租真是帮了大忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我想差不多该回宿舍了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方跟和子结了婚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我会去你们家玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们说了一样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hethna（栅）的魔法阵…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠都
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取下了面具？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个印记
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 沉醉就是逆日死巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 我也驯化了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.47,0:20:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点 和子 和子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠都
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.65,0:20:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是逆日死巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你应该明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们巫女的任务是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经获得了永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的一切都将献给须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星剑 绿松石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠都
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 Samekh复活的时刻到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.87,0:22:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.12,0:24:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 驭星者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.23,0:24:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.55,0:24:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.49,0:24:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是没和你相遇该多好
